Mera Mann by Juss, featuring the talented Parul Gulati, is a soulful Punjabi track produced by the renowned MixSingh and brought to life through the visionary direction of Robby Singh. The music video unfolds a unique storyline where a girl, lost in her dreams, manifests Juss as a superstar. videos.title: Connecting Creators Connecting Countries-M.M Keeravaani, K.S.Chitra, Shankar M, Sonu N, Shreya G
videos.description:
The Waves of India album celebrates India‚Äôs rich cultural tapestry and diversity and will be launched by Honourable Prime Minister of India, Shri Narendra Modi at the  World Audio Visual & Entertainment Summit (WAVES) summit which seeks to celebrate and empower the country‚Äôs Media and Entertainment industry. The album brings together India‚Äôs jewels ‚Äì AR Rahman, Shankar Mahadevan, Prasoon Joshi, MM Keeravani, Ricky Kej and Meet Bros ‚Äì who have on multiple occasions through their art brought numerous global laurels for the country. Each of the aforementioned legends have individual songs which seek to celebrate India‚Äôs cultural heritage in different shapes and form. Each song is binded together through the phrase ‚ÄúSatyam, Shivam, Sundaram‚Äù ‚Äì which signifies the core values of Truth, Auspiciousness, and Beauty. Satyam, Shivam, Sundaram is the foundation of a myriad principles of the Indian culture. The album will instil a deep sense of pride in every Indian.

videos.title: Dhoop Mein Nikla Na Karo (Lyrical Video) | Asha Bhosle | Kishore Kumar
videos.description:
Get ready to bask in the golden melodies of yesteryears as Revibe proudly presents "#DhoopMeinNiklaNaKaro," an enchanting duet by the legendary #AshaBhosle and #KishoreKumar. This timeless track is a musical treasure that will transport you back in time, evoking feelings of nostalgia and romance.

With Asha Bhosle's dulcet tones harmonizing with Kishore Kumar's soulful vocals, "Dhoop Mein Nikla Na Karo" is a symphony of love and longing that transcends generations. The song's poetic lyrics and melodious composition make it an enduring masterpiece that has stood the test of time.
